<div class="leader-topic-suggestion-card">
  {{#if topicSuggestions.length}}
    {{#each topicSuggestions}}
      <h4 class="leader-topic-suggestion-title">suggested new topic: {{this.topicTitle}}</h4>
      <p class="leader-topic-suggestion-meta">
        Submitted on {{formatDate this.submittedAt}} |
        {{#if this.approved}}
          <span class="approved">âœ… Approved</span><br>
          Estimated library release: {{formatDate this.expectedLibraryDate}}
        {{else}}
          <span class="pending">ðŸ•“ Approval pending</span>
        {{/if}}
      </p>
      <div class="leader-topic-suggestion-grid">
        <div class="leader-topic-suggestion-col">
          <h5>1. How has this topic evolved? Why is it especially important now?</h5>
          <p>{{this.paragraph1}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="leader-topic-suggestion-col">
          <h5>2. How does this topic fit in the world of technical services?</h5>
          <p>{{this.paragraph2}}</p>
